---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Services">
  <section class="pt-28 pb-20 sm:pb-28 px-6">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-12 sm:gap-16">
        <div class="sm:col-span-1">
          <p class="reveal visible text-xs font-medium tracking-[0.15em] text-vert uppercase">Services</p>
          <h1 class="reveal visible reveal-delay-1 mt-4 text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-[#2d2a24]">Ce que je propose</h1>
          <p class="reveal visible reveal-delay-2 mt-4 text-sm text-[#2d2a24]/50 leading-relaxed">Du site vitrine à l'application complexe, chaque projet est unique.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="reveal visible reveal-delay-3 mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 bg-vert text-white text-sm font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-vert/90 transition-all duration-200">
            Démarrer
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="sm:col-span-2 space-y-10">
          <div class="reveal visible">
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#2d2a24]">WordPress</h2>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[#2d2a24]/50 leading-relaxed max-w-lg">
              Thème sur mesure, WooCommerce, plugins. Je construis chaque site depuis zéro, pas de template pré-fait. Design sur mesure, performance optimisée.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="text-xs text-vert bg-vert/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Thème sur mesure</span>
              <span class="text-xs text-vert bg-vert/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">WooCommerce</span>
              <span class="text-xs text-vert bg-vert/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Performance</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="reveal visible reveal-delay-1">
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#2d2a24]">Développement sur mesure</h2>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[#2d2a24]/50 leading-relaxed max-w-lg">
              Next.js, Astro, React, Node.js. Des sites ultra-rapides aux applications dynamiques. Stack moderne, déploiement continu.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="text-xs text-vert bg-vert/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Next.js / Astro</span>
              <span class="text-xs text-vert bg-vert/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">React / TypeScript</span>
              <span class="text-xs text-vert bg-vert/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Vercel</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="reveal visible reveal-delay-2">
            <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#2d2a24]">Maintenance & Évolution</h2>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[#2d2a24]/50 leading-relaxed max-w-lg">
              Audit technique, mises à jour de sécurité, amélioration des performances. Je reprends aussi des sites existants pour les moderniser.
            </p>
            <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="text-xs text-vert bg-vert/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Audit & Sécurité</span>
              <span class="text-xs text-vert bg-vert/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Migration</span>
              <span class="text-xs text-vert bg-vert/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Performance</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-vert py-20 sm:py-28 px-6">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white">Vous ne savez pas par où commencer ?</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-white/70">On en parle 30 minutes sans engagement.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-5 py-2.5 bg-jaune text-[#2d2a24] text-sm font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-jaune/90 transition-all duration-200">
          Réserver un appel
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
